Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.13,0:00:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.14,0:00:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.52,0:00:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you just have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words\Nlured men to the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in pursuit of dreams greater\Nthan they've ever dared
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to imagine! This is the time\Nknown as the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.76,0:01:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.22,0:01:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.47,0:01:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.85,0:01:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.24,0:01:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.71,0:01:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NSound the alarm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here and they're\Ngonna kill us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates! Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates are attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody run for your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.28,0:02:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates! Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N"The Honorable Liar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Usopp!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's absolutely\Nno way we'll make it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Grand Line\Nin this condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY,ZORO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, we're gonna\Nneed a whole lot more meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Eating fruit\Neveryday is for the birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll also need\Nsome booze. [grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NShut up, you boneheads! Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand Line's\Na dangerous place
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll need more than beer\Nand meat to survive there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention the place\Nis crawling with pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,who are also in search\Nof the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and they all have ships that\Nare way better than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And we don't have a crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] We don't have a crew,\Nwe don't have any equipment,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.34,0:03:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,or even a real ship\Nfor that matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There is now way we'll\Never make it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, we'll need a cook
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and maybe a musician\Nto keep us entertained.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A musician? [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NSo... stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A little to the south of here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is an island with some\Nsettlements on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And it looks like
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we might be able to get our ship
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and some of the supplies\Nwe need there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Fresh meat at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And lot's of booze, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NIs that all you think about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! What am I gonna\Ndo with you two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NThe pirates are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The pirates are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Run if you want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be here any minute now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! [panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The killers are on the shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Their bloodlust is unquenchable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...we're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NThe pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,are a...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NThat hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You little liar! You're not\Ngonna get away this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This little game is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[VILLAGERS yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NJust try and catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,--C'mon slow pokes! [laughs]\N--[VILLAGERS yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, man! Looks like\Nhe got away again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid's a no\Ngood troublemaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd better hope I\Nnever get a hold of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like nobody's getting\Na hold of him today. Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Yet another job well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It is my solemn duty to send
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the wind of excitement through\Nthis boring, old village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER]\NThere he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:05:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you guys! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER] I bid you good\Nmorning, Captain Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear not! Your loyal crew,\Nthe Usopp Pirates, have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.27,0:06:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pepper, Carrot. It's just\Nyou two? Where's Onion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen him around today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NSound the alarm!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here! They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here and they're\Ngonna kill us all! Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Onion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he's\Nfreaking out about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates! Pirates are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Run for your lives! Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.71,0:06:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Bloodthirsty murderers have\Nlanded! Run everybody, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION panting]\NI'm not playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NEh...It's for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's for real!\NPirates are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! Gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... time for me\Nto have my snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS]\NYou chicken!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NActually, I'm sick! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have, "I'll-die-if-I-\Ndon't-eat-my-snackiosis".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER, ONION]\NYou liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You always told us that you\Nwanted to become real pirate
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,someday, and now's our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER]\NYeah! What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a pirate is\Nafraid of other pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If I recall correctly,\Nit was Buggy the Clown's mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NB-Buggy the Clown?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NUh...I think I'll just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I only saw two tiny boats!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And there were\Njust three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's go time, Brave\NUsopp Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We do have a village to protect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, men! Move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS]\NUh...Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NAhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels good to be\Non dry land again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] There's a village\Nsomewhere around here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] Yeah... It looks\Nlike small one, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOoh! Ooh! Then, there's meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:07:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:08:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be a place to\Neat meat in this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just forget about meat\Nfor a minute, would ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[rustling]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO yawns]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NCareful...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...we're being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? By who? Where are\Nthey? They got meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,--[NAMI screaming]\N--[LUFFY yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOhh! That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this supposed to be\Nwhen we're impressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP laughing]\NI am Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Leader of the invincible\Nnation of pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,who reign over this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You stand before\Na living legend,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the most revered\Npirate who ever lived!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the Great Captain Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NAhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you know that plotting\Nan attack on this island
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,would mean certain death!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My army of 80 million super-mean
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,pirate soldiers would\Nsquash you like bugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NYou expect us to believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! She knows!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! Well, now I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I have\Nbeen so dumb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I practically told\Nher I was lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I am such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NUhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! He was lying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NCurse you, you crafty tactician!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,80 million may have\Nbeen an exaggeration,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have a great many\Nmen under my control!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS whimper]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My guess is three.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS screaming]\NShe does know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.95,0:09:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where're you\Nguys going? Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] A pirate using\Na slingshot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now I've seen it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:10:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing] That's pretty cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth or\NI'll shut it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a proud man and\NI won't stand for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your\Nlast warning,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,or you'll get to see\Nwhy they call me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"Proud Usopp", and not\N"Pushover Usopp".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already seen for yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,just how good I am\Nwith this thing, so,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you know I could rival\Nanyone carrying a pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've drawn your\Npistol, are you willing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Guns aren't for\Nthreats, they're for actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you willing\Nto risk your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] I can assure you,\Nwe're real pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider your next\Nmove very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've drawn your\Npistol, are you willing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Guns aren't for threats,\Nthey're for actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you willing\Nto risk your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP grunting, gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah. Real pirates definitely\Nhave a lot more punch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,behind their words, 'cause\Nthey can actually back 'em up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cool....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY, ZORO laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I stole that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] I stole those words\Nfrom Red Haired Shanks,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,a pirate I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Red Haired Shanks?\NYou really are a real pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you gotta be lying,\Ndo you really know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! I know your dad too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,His name's Yasopp right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP laughs, yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NUh... You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My old man's name is Yasopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But, how?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How in the world\Ndo you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NThis is good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I met your dad when\NI was just a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, does my old\Nman really know Shanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Know him?! When I met your dad\Nhe was a part of Shanks's crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so they were probably\Npretty good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My old man, sailing the high\Nseas with famous pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] I haven't heard\Nfrom him in a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll bet he's\Nstill with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a heck of\Na sharpshooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd keep him on my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Good shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, That's nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I could shoot an ant between\Nthe eyes from across town!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[YASOPP]\NAh! You know something, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a kid named Usopp,\Nand he's just about your age!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me about him already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A hundred times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A hundred?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tellin' ya again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It broke my heart to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had to go.\NYou see, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When the pirate flag beckons,\Nyou must heed it's call!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES CHEER]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to go on and on\Nand on about his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I heard enough about\Nyou to make my ears bleed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And lemme tell you,\Nhe was a great pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure am proud\Nof my old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He leapt into a pirate's\Nlife on the endless sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.07,0:15:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And chose a life\Nof real adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you can help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know someone who could\Nprovide us with a decent ship;
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,or even anyone who knows\Nhow to sail for that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP sighs] Well, It's a\Npretty small village...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I just don't think\Nwe'll be able to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWhat about that huge mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NEe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The one on top of\Nthat hill over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Do you know them, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,With all that money, surely they\Ncould help us get our boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay away from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI, LUFFY, ZORO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered something\Nthat I really gotta do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody knows\Nme at this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh, stay and eat\Nas much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh, gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was he in such a\Nhurry to get outta here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE]\NYou wish to see Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't start this, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,May I see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I like talking to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] No, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That man is, without a\Ndoubt, a chronic liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,For someone in your\Nweakened state,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp's outlandish stories\Nmight be too much to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your late parents instructed\Nme to protect you to the fullest
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,of my abilities. It would\Nbe against their wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,for you to see him, Miss Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, I'll leave\Nyour medicine right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be sure to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Killjoy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE]\N"Killjoy" will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A name I'll bear,\Nif you are kept safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,--[KAYA whimpers]\N--[doors clatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NPardon the intrusion... Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp! You came!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! How are you?\NYou seem a little down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NI guess I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of talking like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to invite inside\Nlike a proper guest,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's just no way\NKlahadore would ever allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a bad person, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, I'm a brave\Nwarrior of the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,who likes endless\Noceans and the open sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Houses weren't made\Nfor rogues like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd probably just feel\Ncramped in there. [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what adventure are you\Ngoing to tell me about today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHmm. Well let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the story of me\Nfighting a giant goldfish
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,at the south pole, when\NI was only five years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NA goldfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NA giant goldfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What first astounded me was\Nthe immense size of it's poop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so big that\Nwhen I landed on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was solid ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked like an island!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP, KAYA laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this\Nis the place they took him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, those terrible\Npirates dragged him inside
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and now it's up to us\Nto save our captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But, guys, those're\Nreal pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What if they've grilled\Nand eaten him already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's grisly old witch hags who\Neat their victims, not pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,OK you guys, this\Ntime it's for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:18:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS gulp]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be the most brutal\Nand epic battle of our lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,we must show no mercy because\Nthey will never show it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS]\NHm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS] The Usopp\Npirates, have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY] Huh?\N--Who're these kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Usopp is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.31,0:19:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Fess up, you filthy pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done with\Nour beloved Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION, CARROT]\NYeah! Tell us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY sighs]\NThat meat sure was good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,--[KIDS gasp]\N--What meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,These pirates are cannibals!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done, you savages?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] If you're looking\Nfor your captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...we ate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS]\NWah! Cannibals!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you punks\Nlooking at me for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY, ZORO laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] You just had to say\Nsomething stupid, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER laughs]\NYou really had us going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhoa! This place is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And If our captain\Nran off at this hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,then this is the\Nplace he's gonna be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... What in the world\Ndoes Usopp come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He comes to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To lie? That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER]\NHe's not a bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's great! Isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! He's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How is a liar awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER] Well, Kaya,\Nthe girl who lives there,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,has been in a terrible\Ndepression that's kept
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,her weak and in bed since\Nher parents got sick
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and died a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She's very rich,\Nbut all that money
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't help her\Nrecover from her sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION] So our captain tells\Nhis special made-up stories
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to make her laugh\Nand cheer her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT] Captain Usopp is\Nthe best at telling lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that really is\Npretty nice of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS]\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The best thing about\Nhim is his mischievous side,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.49,0:20:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,he's always up to something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I like him 'cause he's\Nnot afraid to be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I like the\NCaptain's crazy lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So when he tells\Nher those stories,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,he makes her feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NYep! Lot's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.42,0:21:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Great! I think we should\Nask her for a ship after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not the ones who make\Nher feel better, Usopp is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NGetting in is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guards at the gate\Ndon't let anyone through!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,--[ALL] Uhh...\N--[CARROT] Where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,--I'll go ask her!\N--[ALL gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.77,0:21:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NNo! You're not gonna--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NGum-gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.48,0:21:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,His arms are all stretchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's some kind of monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon the intrusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORRO]\NN-No, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,--LUFFY] Rocket!\N--[ALL yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] So after that terrifying\Nand traumatic little incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.91,0:21:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,we escaped into the sky riding\Non a giant slingshot ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHm? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.63,0:21:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:21:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NThat worked well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.97,0:22:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, real well!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.56,0:22:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Don't mind them Kaya,\Nthis happens to me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the price of\Nbeing a famous adventurer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.61,0:22:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just new recruits\Nwho heard about me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and came to join\Nthe Usopp pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.40,0:22:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, not me. I came\Nhere to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.99,0:22:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A favor? From me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NUh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.41,0:22:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if\Nthere was any way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.12,0:22:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,--you could help us geta boat.\N--[KLAHADORE] You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.96,0:22:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Klahadore...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.17,0:22:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.76,0:22:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you know that this\Nis criminal trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey guys, who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.01,0:23:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.89,0:23:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.60,0:23:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.11,0:23:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.82,0:23:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.38,0:23:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.67,0:23:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.51,0:24:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.55,0:24:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.52,0:24:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.77,0:24:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.65,0:24:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.87,0:24:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] Who does that\Nbutler think he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.53,0:24:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,treating us like\Nbunch of thieves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.58,0:24:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Yeah! We only\Nsnuck in to get a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.41,0:24:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Hate to break it to\Nyou Nami, but we are thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.25,0:24:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] Well, that weird guy\Nis way more suspicious than us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.88,0:24:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHm? What's with that ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.13,0:24:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHey, look! The butlers with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.67,0:24:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.97,0:24:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.59,0:24:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Weirdest Guy Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.35,0:24:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Jango the Hypnotist!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.10,0:24:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

